subSubSection.paragraph:
Variation.
Degrees of melanism varies in this species (
Figs. 168–171
). Two individuals observed lack of pronotal tomentous band (
Figs. 169–170
). Only one female is heavily tomentous and has narrow lateral bands on elytra.
